{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 440469, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "可能是单纯羡慕资源好吧，有一说一，我也羡慕，但也不酸，毕竟高考拉垮。", "timestamp": 1602503830, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440477, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "主要是新雅培养出来的学生并没有表现的更好，但享受了种种特权，大家觉得德不配位", "timestamp": 1602503964, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440483, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "并且很多理工科院系的同学觉得新雅的培养方案就是在浪费学生的时间", "timestamp": 1602504041, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440495, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: emmm，您所说的表现的更好，是哪方面的表现呢？ 素质，能力还是人际交往？", "timestamp": 1602504244, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440500, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 当然是专业能力", "timestamp": 1602504329, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440506, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 懂了", "timestamp": 1602504410, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440510, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 新雅人儿在此。无用之用方为大用吧，看自己信不信了。大部分人高考分的确也配得上现在的政策…？", "timestamp": 1602504468, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440589, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 跟通识教育比专业能力可还行", "timestamp": 1602505312, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440599, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 但是新雅获得的特权（例如推研）是以考察专业能力为基本的，这是不是有些不公平呢？", "timestamp": 1602505450, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440604, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 高考分确实...但是这种特权到大四保研还存在，就不是很合理了", "timestamp": 1602505493, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440614, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果新雅像姚班一样出一个陈立杰式的人物，那么大家就会对新雅心服口服了", "timestamp": 1602505558, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440619, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 这是不同的教育理念之间的矛盾，新雅这样的通识教育在国内的大环境下本来就是个怪胎，为了维持这方试验田有时候不得不牺牲一些别的东西。不过cz也并不觉得新雅同学德不配位", "timestamp": 1602505667, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 440639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 毕竟是甘愿做试验品，享受特权补偿是理所应当的，但是享受的同时也得忍受其他同学的非议了。", "timestamp": 1602505882, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 499939, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 91432, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 牺牲一年时间学通识课，得花三年修完你们四年的课，本身就难，通识课给分还低，这怎么卷的过你们呢？", "timestamp": 1603971712, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 91432, "reply": 14, "tag": null, "text": "真诚提问，为什么好多人总对新雅阴阳怪气的啊，感觉敌意好重", "timestamp": 1602503747, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1606782631, "url": "", "vote": {}}}